{
  "chapter": 34,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十四回　真相大白。连城璧向萧十一郎揭露了一切真相：他就是天宗第二代主人，从垂死的逍遥侯口中得到了天宗秘密后重组天宗，借萧十一郎之手清除叛徒，又假扮瞎子将责任推给冰冰。他故意捧高萧十一郎再令他跌落谷底，目的就是要让他生不如死。萧十一郎看似已彻底被毁，但金剑上被改的字迹显示一切可能都是萧十一郎的反间计。二人在鸿宾酒楼对峙后，在峡谷中决战。萧十一郎放下了割鹿刀，令连城璧陷入空虚与恐惧，最终击败了连城璧。萧十一郎离去时留下一句：你不能死，因为我还是欠你的。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "走，我们喝酒去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你的酒量好像又精进多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你一天要喝多少酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "越多越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "三坛够不够？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "马马虎虎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们以前并不能算是朋友，可是以前的事都已过去了，现在……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在我本该多陪你两天，却非走不可，我只能留下一百坛酒给你，让你尽一月之欢，一月之后，我再来看你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我们以前也许并不是朋友，但现在却已是朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我们现在真的已经是朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你流泪，是不是因为感激我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这是你的刀，现在还是你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刀还是同样的刀，可是我呢？我已变成了什么东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你知不知道你怎么会变成这样子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你不知道，一定不知道，因为……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "因为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为真正知道这秘密的，天下只有一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "一个你永远想不到的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你变成这样子，完全都是我害你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你知道不知道谁才是真正的天宗主人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错，就是我，所有的一切计划，都是我一个人想出来的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "去看他？为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为我知道他绝不会就这么样轻易死在下面的，这世上假如真有一个人能有两条命，这一个人一定就是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你下去的时候，他真的还没有死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你想救他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我想救的，并不是他的人，而是他的秘密。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "每个人都有秘密，像他这种人的秘密，对别人来说已不止是一种宝藏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "他的秘密，也就是天宗的秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "他将这秘密告诉了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "他既然还没有死，为什么会把这秘密告诉你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为他不能不说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你实在变了，变得太迟钝，这句话你本来不该问的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为你本该想得到，他若不说，就只有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "他说出来之后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这句话你也不该问的，他说出来之后，死得当然更快。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我知道他的秘密后，就立刻又将天宗重新组织起来，只可惜天宗里还有些人不肯接受我的命令，所以我就故意让那些人在你和冰冰面前出现，我知道冰冰一定会让你杀了他们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这本就是借刀杀人，一石二鸟之计。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我本来也有很多机会杀你的，你自己也应该知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你知不知道我为什么一直都没有下手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为我要让你活着比死更痛苦，我要彻底毁了你，我要让每个人都对你完全绝望，我要让每个人都认为你是个无可救药的畜生。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我用尽了一切方法，先让你的声名，财富，地位，都达到巅峰，然后再让你掉下来，利用你作工具，替我除去了那些叛徒，这两点你现在一定已经想通了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我本来还想到你到八仙船去，替我杀了最后那几个叛徒，只有那一次的计划，我没有完全成功。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "可是到了那时候，世上已没有任何人，任何事能阻挡我，你就算不去，我也一样可以自己动手。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "所以你故意让我错过了，因为你觉得你自己动手更方便。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我的确喜欢自己动手，无论什么事都是一样。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "那瞎子也是你扮成的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我要让你有一种错觉，认为那瞎子就是逍遥侯，认为逍遥侯还没有死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为我要把这所有的责任，都推到冰冰身上。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "冰冰……冰冰……她真是个可怕的女孩子。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这一切计划大功告成之后，冰冰和逍遥侯就可以真的死了，这世上也就不会再有人知道我的秘密，更不会有人怀疑到我就是天宗的主人，所以我还是跟以前一样，是白璧无瑕，侠义无双的连城璧。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你为什么要把这些事告诉我？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "因为我要让你痛苦，我要让你自己也觉得自己是个无可救药的呆子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "现在我要走了，那一百坛酒，我还留给你，可是你最好记住，那也许是你一生之中最后的欢乐，喝完了这一百坛酒之后，你怎么还能活得下去？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燃薰香、备兰汤、设盛宴、传鼓乐！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "是好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "酒，替你做了很多事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
